(* Proof:
   By finite induction on s.
   Base: PPROD {} ** n = PPIMAGE (\p. p ** n) {}
      LHS = PPROD {} ** n
          = |1| ** n             by poly_prod_set_empty
          = |1|                  by poly_one_exp
      RHS = PPIMAGE (\p. p ** n) {}
          = PPROD (IMAGE (\p. p ** n) {})   by notation
          = PPROD {}             by IMAGE_EMPTY
